locs.text: prati ghante stok jaanakaaree praapt karata hai
laghu kampanee prateek
apanee alphavantagai api kunjee darj karen
krpaya apanee api kunjee pradaan karen.
pradarshan api kunjee ka upayog nahin kiya ja sakata.
aapakee api kunjee 16 varnon kee honee chaahie.
stok deta praapt karate samay koee truti huee. atirikt jaanakaaree yahaan paee ja sakatee hai
shuruaatee stok keemat
uchch stok keemat
kam stok keemat
band stok keemat
stok volyoom
api kunjee aavashyak hai. setings se konfigar karen.
koee stok deta upalabdh nahin hai.
yah anubhaag aapako stok konfigar karane deta hai.
api kunjee
alphavantagai stok api ke lie kunjee
kampanee kod
stok kampanee
setings pravishtiyaan praapt karane mein viphal.
stok jaanakaaree nahin mil sakatee.
